text:
South Pacific Tourism Exchange 2016 heading to Gold Coast Australia   
Sep 03, 2015 eTN   
The South Pacific Tourism Exchange (SPTE) will be heading to the Gold Coast in Australia on May 20 and 21, 2016. 
The South Pacific Tourism Organization (SPTO) made the announcement in Suva today. 
After hosting a successful SPTE 2015 at the Melbourne Convention Centre in Australia this year, the regionâ€™s premier tourism marketing and development authority made the decision to take the annual tourism expo up north after consultations with its members and stakeholders.
